actor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Partnerships</th><td><a href="/wiki/Trevor_Fitzroy" title="Trevor Fitzroy">Chronomancer</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Notable aliases</th><td>Askante</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Abilities</th><td>Energy blasts, intangibility (holographic Shard only)</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Shard Bishop</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Mutant_(Marvel_Comics)" title="Mutant (Marvel Comics)">mutant</a> fictional character appearing in <a href="/wiki/American_comic_book" title="American comic book">American comic books</a> published by <a href="/wiki/Marvel_Comics" title="Marvel Comics">Marvel Comics</a>.
</p>
